metadata.name: Writers Room: Yacht Key
metadata.description: Writers Room is an interoperable contentverse fueled by community creativity to dream, develop, and incubate the future of IP. Owning a Writers Room NFT grants membership access to leverage your character(s) IP in various media projects; govern a collection of popular web3 native character IP including Jenkins the Valet, Jenkins the Mutant, and Goodboy; access exclusive partnership opportunties and IRL/Digital holder experiences; and create and develop your character's IP with the ability to earn rewards and prizes for your content
